<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Konrad Tafler, Bürger zu Nürnberg</head><p>Der Rat lädt Tafler vor.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_346" id="172v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_346_r1l13"><expan>Conrad<ex>en</ex></expan> Tafler </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_346_r1l14"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> Burger </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_346_r1l15"><expan>Vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> freuntſchaft beuor / Conrad Taffler vvir heiſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_346_r1l16">vnd gepıeten dir bey deinem eyde den du vns geſworen haſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_346_r1l17"><expan>vven<ex>n</ex></expan> du diſen <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> brief <expan>geſeh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>v<ex>er</ex>hört</expan> habſt / daʒ du </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_346_r1l18">niht laſʒeſt du kumſt herheim für vns / <expan>vvan<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir etvvaʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_346_r1l19">notlichs mit dir cʒu reden <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / als du <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>neme<ex>n</ex></expan> vvırdeſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_346_r1l20"><expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> Jn die <expan>ſ<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan> Dyoniſij </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_346" id="172v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Conrad<ex>en</ex></expan> Tafler, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
                        burger </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Uns<ex>er</ex></expan> freuntschaft bevor. Conrad Taffler, wir
                        heissen und gepieten dir bey deinem eyde, den du uns gesworen hast,
                                <expan>wen<ex>n</ex></expan> du disen <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        brief <expan>geseh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und <expan>v<ex>er</ex>hört</expan>
                        habst, daz du niht laszest, du kumst herheim für uns,
                            <expan>wan<ex>n</ex></expan> wir etwaz notlichs mit dir czu reden
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, als du <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>neme<ex>n</ex></expan> wirdest.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in die
                            <expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan> Dyonisii.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
